---
/**
 * /terms — Terms and Conditions (SMS messaging program scope).
 *
 * Built 2026-05-05 from the live twistedpin.com terms-and-conditions
 * page (user screenshot). The live page is narrowly scoped to the
 * SMS messaging program — TCPA / CTIA compliance scaffold, not a
 * full website-use ToS. Preserving that scope here so we don't
 * silently broaden the legal commitments without ops review.
 *
 * Structural note: if a broader ToS is needed pre-launch (covering
 * website use, reservation cancellation, gift card terms, prize /
 * promotion rules, governing law, liability disclaimers), it should
 * either:
 *   (a) live on a separate /terms-of-use page and link to here from
 *       the SMS section, OR
 *   (b) replace this page with a comprehensive ToS that retains the
 *       SMS sections at the back
 * Flagging in launch-checklist.md for ops decision.
 *
 * Voice: legal copy stays factual / formal — no voice-rule reframes
 * needed. Section headings tightened to t2 register; substance
 * preserved exactly to keep TCPA/CTIA compliance language intact.
 *
 * Last Updated date matches the live page until ops confirms a new
 * effective date for this rebuild.
 */
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import SnapFooter from "../components/snap/SnapFooter.astro";

const LAST_UPDATED = "February 21, 2026";
---
<Base
  title="Terms and Conditions — Twisted Pin Plainfield IL"
  description="Terms and Conditions for the Twisted Pin SMS messaging program. Opt-in, opt-out, message frequency, eligibility, and contact information. Plainfield, IL."
>

  <section class="t2-hero" data-hero aria-labelledby="terms-h1">
    <div class="t2-hero-copy">
      <p class="t-eyebrow hero-fade" data-delay-ms="0">Twisted Pin · SMS Messaging Program</p>
      <h1 class="t-display t2-hero-headline hero-fade" id="terms-h1" data-delay-ms="120">
        Terms &amp; Conditions.
      </h1>
      <p class="t2-hero-sub hero-fade" data-delay-ms="320">
        Last updated {LAST_UPDATED}. The terms below govern the
        Twisted Pin SMS messaging program. By submitting your phone
        number through our event inquiry form, you agree to these
        terms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="t2-section legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-h2-1">
    <div class="t2-section-inner">
      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-1">1. Overview</h2>
      <p>These Terms and Conditions govern your use of the Twisted Pin SMS messaging program. By submitting your phone number through our event inquiry form, you agree to these terms. Please read them carefully before participating.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-2">2. Program Description</h2>
      <p>Twisted Pin ("Twisted Pin", "we", "us") operates an SMS messaging program to communicate with customers who have submitted event inquiry forms. Program messages may include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Responses to event booking inquiries</li>
        <li>Custom event quotes and pricing information</li>
        <li>Availability confirmations and booking details</li>
        <li>Customer service follow-up related to your event</li>
        <li>Event reminders and confirmations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-3">3. How to Opt In</h2>
      <p>You opt in to receive SMS messages from Twisted Pin by submitting your phone number through our event inquiry form at twistedpin.com. By providing your phone number and submitting the form, you expressly consent to receive text messages from Twisted Pin at the number provided. You confirm that you are the account holder or have the account holder's permission to enroll the number.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-4">4. Message Frequency</h2>
      <p>Message frequency varies based on your inquiry and the nature of your event planning process. You may receive multiple messages per inquiry as we assist you with quotes, availability, and booking details. We will not send unsolicited promotional messages unrelated to your event inquiry.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-5">5. Message and Data Rates</h2>
      <p>Message and data rates may apply. These charges are billed by your mobile carrier and are not collected by Twisted Pin. Please contact your mobile carrier if you are unsure about your messaging and data plan rates.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-6">6. How to Opt Out (STOP)</h2>
      <p>You may opt out of receiving SMS messages from Twisted Pin at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message you receive from us.</p>
      <p>After texting STOP, you will receive one final confirmation message and no further messages will be sent. To re-enroll, simply submit a new event inquiry form or text START to our number.</p>
      <p>Other opt-out keywords we honor: STOPALL, UNSUBSCRIBE, CANCEL, END, QUIT.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-7">7. How to Get Help (HELP)</h2>
      <p>For help or more information, reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message or contact us directly at:</p>
      <ul class="legal-contact">
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contactus@twistedpin.com">contactus@twistedpin.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> 815-782-7790</li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> Twisted Pin, 15610 Joliet Rd, Plainfield, IL 60544</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-8">8. Privacy</h2>
      <p>Your phone number and personal information collected through our SMS program will be used solely to respond to your event inquiry and facilitate your booking with Twisted Pin. We do not sell, rent, or share your phone number with third parties for marketing purposes. For full details on how we collect and use your data, please review our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-9">9. Eligibility</h2>
      <p>This SMS program is available to users with a valid mobile phone number in the United States. By opting in, you represent that you are 18 years of age or older and are the account holder of the mobile number provided, or have authorization from the account holder to enroll.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-10">10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>Twisted Pin reserves the right to modify these Terms and Conditions at any time. Changes will be posted at twistedpin.com/terms/. Continued participation in the SMS program after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2 class="legal-h2" id="terms-h2-11">11. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about these Terms and Conditions or our SMS program, please contact us:</p>
      <ul class="legal-contact">
        <li><strong>Twisted Pin</strong></li>
        <li>15610 Joliet Rd, Plainfield, IL 60544</li>
        <li><a href="mailto:contactus@twistedpin.com">contactus@twistedpin.com</a></li>
        <li><a href="/">twistedpin.com</a></li>
      </ul>

      <p class="legal-jurisdiction">Twisted Pin is located in Plainfield, Illinois and serves the greater Chicagoland area. Our SMS program is operated in compliance with TCPA regulations and CTIA messaging guidelines.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SnapFooter />
</Base>

<style>
  /* Same legal-page recipe as /privacy — see that file for the
     vocabulary. Hoisting to global.css if a third legal page lands
     (rule of three). */
  .legal-section .t2-section-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .legal-h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 22px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: var(--warm-white);
    margin: 40px 0 14px;
  }
  .legal-h2:first-child { margin-top: 8px; }
  @media (min-width: 760px) {
    .legal-h2 { font-size: 26px; margin-top: 48px; }
  }

  .legal-section p,
  .legal-section li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--warm-mid);
  }
  .legal-section p { margin: 0 0 14px; }

  .legal-section ul {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    padding-left: 22px;
  }
  .legal-section li { margin-bottom: 6px; }

  .legal-section strong { color: var(--warm-white); font-weight: 700; }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--glow);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .legal-contact {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .legal-jurisdiction {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(244, 239, 227, 0.10);
    font-size: 13px !important;
    color: var(--warm-dim) !important;
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
